<div class="page">
	<div id="content" class="page-container container" style="padding-top:22px">
		<header class="header">
			
			<h1 class="title" align="left">
				厦门鼓浪屿食闽菜 让食客在美食中了解闽南文化。
			</h1>
			<div class="desc">
				<img src="//om.gtimg.cn/om/om_3.0/h5_detail/images/logo_qiehao.png" class="logo">
				<span class="author">大脸猫带你吃遍世界</span>
				<span class="date">2019-11-16</span>
			</div>
			
		</header>
		<section class="article">
			

			

			
		
			
				
					
						<p>厦门的味道，是沙茶的浓烈，是海鲜的鲜甜，是薄饼的融合，是花生汤的甜蜜。鼓浪屿上这家闽菜餐厅，主打传家闽南菜，保留古早味，食材新鲜优质，价格实惠，人均七八十就可以吃得很好。让食客在享受美食的同时感受闽南文化。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778470472/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778470472/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>———营业信息———</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>地理位置：鼓浪屿龙头路300号。</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>营业信息：11:00-16:00，17:00-22:00；</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778470473/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778470473/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778470474/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778470474/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>———菜品———</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>鼓浪屿林家薄饼：</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>薄饼，闽南传统小吃，分为饼皮和内馅。以烫面放在铁盘上烙出饼皮，看似简单但要求饼皮薄而有韧性，包馅时方能不破。馅料大多以包菜、瘦肉丝、豆腐干丝、海蛎、胡萝卜丝等炒制。林四喜的薄饼是将皮和馅料摆一盘端出，让食客自己包裹，加料丰俭由人且更有趣味性。比较特别的是酱料里多了芥末酱，喜欢呛鼻的可以加一点，十分过瘾。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778470475/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778470475/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778470476/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778470476/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>本港石斑鱼头汤：</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>选用新鲜石斑鱼头炖出一锅好鱼汤。石斑鱼头经过煎制，慢火炖煮后，鲜味完全释放入汤中，口感鲜嫩，皮Q有胶质感。汤呈奶白色，喝一口鲜美暖胃，可以自己适量加点胡椒粉，去腥的同时更能激发鱼汤的鲜。也可以选择有面线的套餐，面线饱吸鱼汤，爽滑入味。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471026/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471026/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471027/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471027/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>闽南套肠鲜笋煲：</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>套肠是将猪小肠好几层叠套在一起，自制的套肠套的很紧实，口感脆嫩。常规是搭配酸菜等重口味菜，想不到跟鲜笋搭配也很出色。挑选的最嫩的鲜笋，脆爽鲜嫩，吃起来十分清爽。煲的做法让两种食材的味道更加融合。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471028/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471028/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471029/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471029/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>四喜沙茶锅：</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>沙茶锅在厦门很多餐厅都有，每家味道也略有不同。这家的沙茶辣度比较淡，稍微甜一点，奶香味更重。里面加了虾、鱿鱼、肉羹、豆腐等。虾每一粒都很大，肉紧实吃的出的新鲜，鱿鱼Q弹脆，肉羹抓了粉口感嫩滑，豆腐泡了沙茶汤特别入味，入口即化。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471030/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471030/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471591/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471591/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471592/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471592/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471594/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471594/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>还有杏林土笋冻，里面加了很多沙虫，给料十足。闽南炸醋肉，外酥里嫩，口感酸甜开胃。四喜甜汤，炖煮的绵软的花生汤加了糯香的芋头，香甜绵软。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471595/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471595/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471596/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778471596/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778472109/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778472109/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778472110/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778472110/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>餐厅环境：怀旧复古风与现代的结合。一共三层的小楼，仿佛去古时大户人家做客。无论是卡座或是圆桌都很宽敞，暖色调灯光温馨舒适使人放松。二楼明档厨房吃得放心。服务员热情亲切，手机扫码点单很方便。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778472111/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778472111/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778472112/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10778472112/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>总结：还原传统闽南传家菜，选用新鲜食材，保留原始烹饪方法。九大招牌菜都是经典。环境温馨舒适，人均七八十性价比高，鼓浪屿上值得推荐的闽味餐厅。</p>
					
				
			
		
			

			

			
			
